1
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:23,340
♪Memories pile up, never fading away♪

2
00:00:23,340 --> 00:00:25,970
♪I call it a sickness—I can't let go♪

3
00:00:26,810 --> 00:00:29,820
♪Missing you cuts deep,
shaping your shadow♪

4
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:32,300
♪All my pain comes
from not wanting to part♪

5
00:00:33,370 --> 00:00:35,010
♪I was caught in the middle♪

6
00:00:35,010 --> 00:00:36,660
♪It's hard to survive♪

7
00:00:36,660 --> 00:00:38,260
♪Love faded in you, but grew in me♪

8
00:00:38,260 --> 00:00:39,940
♪And wore me down inside♪

9
00:00:39,940 --> 00:00:41,540
♪I'm the desert, craving the open sea♪

10
00:00:41,540 --> 00:00:42,940
♪I'll show you the humor in tragedy♪

11
00:00:42,940 --> 00:00:46,190
♪Will you ever remember me?♪

12
00:00:46,190 --> 00:00:51,780
♪The wind flows on, clear like a river♪

13
00:00:52,860 --> 00:00:56,540
♪But me? I'm just stuck being me♪

14
00:00:56,540 --> 00:00:59,250
♪Chasing you, and wandering♪

15
00:00:59,250 --> 00:01:04,700
♪Rain falls, slipping away like wishes♪

16
00:01:05,770 --> 00:01:09,530
♪But my heart stays solid, won't sway♪

17
00:01:09,530 --> 00:01:12,940
♪Love's a flower, doomed to fade♪

18
00:01:12,940 --> 00:01:16,980
=Love Beyond The Curse=

19
00:01:17,020 --> 00:01:19,940
=Episode 16=

20
00:01:24,980 --> 00:01:25,820
Chong Yang.

21
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:36,420
Why is it you?

22
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:39,100
What do you want?

23
00:01:40,380 --> 00:01:42,380
Gu Changsheng, where is this place?

24
00:01:42,940 --> 00:01:44,580
Just stay here on your own.

25
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:46,580
Gu Changsheng!

26
00:01:46,940 --> 00:01:47,780
Gu Changsheng!

27
00:01:50,940 --> 00:01:53,340
Gu Changsheng, where am I?

28
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:06,100
Chong Yang.

29
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:08,820
Where are you?

30
00:02:17,540 --> 00:02:18,740
(She'll probably like this.)

31
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:30,300
(Where's Nanxing?)

32
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:45,100
(My powers are getting weaker.)

33
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:47,820
(I can't sense Nanxing at all.)

34
00:02:49,140 --> 00:02:50,660
(Hope she's not in trouble.)

35
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:52,220
(I have to find her soon.)

36
00:03:04,260 --> 00:03:05,140
Gu Changsheng!

37
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:06,740
Come out, now!

38
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:13,340
Yang.

39
00:03:14,220 --> 00:03:15,060
Where's Nanxing?

40
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:17,860
How should I know?

41
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:21,780
She stayed home with you all day.

42
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:23,340
If you don't know, who does?

43
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:24,980
Yang.

44
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:27,260
Are you doubting me because of her?

45
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:28,780
You don't trust me.

46
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:32,620
I know you so well.

47
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:33,860
That's why I have doubts.

48
00:03:34,540 --> 00:03:35,820
Where is Nanxing, really?

49
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:37,700
What if I don't tell you?

50
00:03:39,740 --> 00:03:40,860
What will you do to me?

51
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:45,020
Kill me?

52
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:49,380
Yang, the Yongye people can't die.

53
00:03:50,780 --> 00:03:51,620
Unless...

54
00:03:52,260 --> 00:03:54,140
someone secretly planted Noctrose.

55
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:57,020
So,

56
00:03:58,260 --> 00:04:00,020
you did hide Nanxing.

57
00:04:00,020 --> 00:04:00,860
Yeah, it was me.

58
00:04:05,420 --> 00:04:06,500
Let me ask you again.

59
00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:10,900
Where is Nanxing?

60
00:04:12,220 --> 00:04:13,060
Yang,

61
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:17,300
I don't want you to go.
I want you here forever.

62
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:41,340
Yang!

63
00:04:45,540 --> 00:04:46,380
Ji Nanxing

64
00:04:48,340 --> 00:04:50,260
is stuck in my boundary on the back hill.

65
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:16,340
Chong Yang.

66
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:19,100
Chong Yang, where are you?

67
00:05:19,310 --> 00:05:22,850
♪Trading sharp words in a fight♪

68
00:05:23,780 --> 00:05:24,620
Nanxing!

69
00:05:28,100 --> 00:05:28,940
Nanxing!

70
00:05:30,590 --> 00:05:33,910
♪Dreaming of a night with him,
lost in haze♪

71
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:37,850
♪Right or wrong, I pour my heart out♪

72
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:39,780
♪And play along with your secret hints♪

73
00:05:39,820 --> 00:05:41,900
(Why is Gu Changsheng doing this to me?)

74
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:43,820
(What did I do so wrong?)

75
00:05:45,730 --> 00:05:47,890
♪In the trap of love,
it's all pitch-black♪

76
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:48,740
Nanxing!

77
00:05:50,740 --> 00:05:51,580
Nanxing!

78
00:05:51,860 --> 00:05:53,100
Nanxing, where are you?

79
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:56,220
Chong Yang.

80
00:05:56,700 --> 00:05:57,540
Chong Yang!

81
00:05:58,140 --> 00:05:59,380
Chong Yang, I'm right here!

82
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:01,100
Nanxing!

83
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:06,180
Chong Yang, I'm really scared.

84
00:06:06,180 --> 00:06:07,220
Don't worry, I'm here now.

85
00:06:07,990 --> 00:06:11,580
♪Once you forgive me, I'll be just like you♪

86
00:06:11,910 --> 00:06:13,980
♪Like bees drawn to flowers♪

87
00:06:13,980 --> 00:06:15,730
♪My defenses were always broken through♪

88
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:17,540
How did we end up here?

89
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:20,140
It's quieter here.

90
00:06:22,900 --> 00:06:23,740
Chong Yang.

91
00:06:24,140 --> 00:06:26,620
When you're not with me,
I get so scared.

92
00:06:26,940 --> 00:06:27,900
Chong Yang.

93
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:30,860
No one will hurt you again.

94
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:36,150
♪Why rush to shield me with kindness?♪

95
00:07:17,580 --> 00:07:18,420
You're awake.

96
00:07:25,340 --> 00:07:27,020
Weren't you waiting for this day?

97
00:07:29,220 --> 00:07:30,140
Now you're getting shy.

98
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:32,620
Who's shy?

99
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:37,820
You were the one waiting for this.

100
00:07:40,820 --> 00:07:41,660
Who was the one

101
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:42,980
always glued to me

102
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:44,500
and wanting to stay with me?

103
00:07:46,220 --> 00:07:47,980
But who was the one
making harsh promises,

104
00:07:47,980 --> 00:07:49,260
yet refusing to let me go?

105
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:03,740
Chong Yang,

106
00:08:05,220 --> 00:08:06,060
thank you.

107
00:08:07,540 --> 00:08:08,860
You didn't just save my life,

108
00:08:10,980 --> 00:08:12,220
and you make me feel

109
00:08:13,660 --> 00:08:16,060
a happiness I've never had before.

110
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:22,820
It's me who should thank you.

111
00:08:24,700 --> 00:08:25,540
For centuries,

112
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:27,900
I lived in the shadows.

113
00:08:29,020 --> 00:08:29,860
Then you showed up,

114
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:34,580
like a ray of light in my darkness.

115
00:08:39,940 --> 00:08:42,340
(Nanxing, I regret it now.)

116
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:44,580
(I don't want to die anymore.)

117
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:47,220
(I'd rather suffer alone myself,)

118
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:48,700
(enduring endless loneliness)

119
00:08:50,100 --> 00:08:51,420
(just to stay by your side)

120
00:08:51,940 --> 00:08:53,100
(and walk this life with you.)

121
00:09:22,570 --> 00:09:27,170
♪Longing finds a heartbeat as I fall♪

122
00:09:27,930 --> 00:09:34,330
♪When our eyes meet, the world softens♪

123
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:38,370
♪I cling to the past like a wanderer♪

124
00:09:38,530 --> 00:09:41,970
♪Still guarding the gate
to old memories♪

125
00:09:42,170 --> 00:09:47,810
♪Eternal promise♪

126
00:09:49,130 --> 00:09:56,010
♪How do I heal after losing you?♪

127
00:09:56,650 --> 00:10:02,930
♪How could I let go of all this pain?♪

128
00:10:04,290 --> 00:10:08,770
♪The more I hold back,
the closer you feel♪

129
00:10:08,970 --> 00:10:12,170
♪The more it hurts,
the more I break♪

130
00:10:12,490 --> 00:10:17,730
♪Every snowflake feels like your kiss♪

131
00:10:18,010 --> 00:10:24,770
♪Let time pause,
let fireflies fill the sky♪

132
00:10:25,210 --> 00:10:31,970
♪In your arms,
I lose focus—tears fall♪

133
00:10:32,850 --> 00:10:37,170
♪And everything else just fades away♪

134
00:10:37,730 --> 00:10:40,610
♪You belong only to me♪

135
00:10:41,250 --> 00:10:46,850
♪Even if we're apart, or worlds away♪

136
00:10:47,330 --> 00:10:49,490
♪None of that could ever matter♪
